@startuml GetOne_Reservation

title Get Single Reservation API Flow

actor User
participant "API Server" as API
database MongoDB

User -> API: GET /api/v1/reservations/{id}\nHeader: Authorization: token
activate API

API -> API: Verify JWT token
API -> MongoDB: Find reservation by ID + populate restaurant
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> API: Return reservation object
deactivate MongoDB

alt Reservation not found
  API --> User: 404 - Reservation not found
else Reservation found
  API -> API: Check authorization\n(if needed)
  
  API -> API: Populate restaurant details
  note right: Include:\n- name\n- address\n- telephone\n- openTime\n- closeTime
  
  API --> User: 200 - Success\n{success: true,\ndata: reservation}
end

deactivate API
